{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 7",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-607890080152945238 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=607864187825160759&sectionId=607890080152945238)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKM12xxoUh_text","label":"ggKM12xxoUh_text","default":"<p><strong>By week 5, my knee pain during yoga was noticeably better.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvVZ9OaVK1_text","label":"ggvVZ9OaVK1_text","default":"<p>I could hold poses I'd been modifying for months.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXymGOyI65_text","label":"ggXymGOyI65_text","default":"<p>Downward dog didn't make my wrists ache. &nbsp;And especially warrior pose didn't make my back throb.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBiUz-K9TI_text","label":"ggBiUz-K9TI_text","default":"<p>Week 6 is when my husband noticed.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzBs6uolvA_text","label":"ggzBs6uolvA_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"You're moving differently,\" he said. \"Like you're not scared of your own body anymore.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8-0fEuMxl_text","label":"gg8-0fEuMxl_text","default":"<p>He was right.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg96mqAe0Vu_text","label":"gg96mqAe0Vu_text","default":"<p><strong>I'd been tiptoeing through my own life. Afraid every movement might cause a fracture.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggSiGoTJmg_text","label":"gggSiGoTJmg_text","default":"<p>That constant fear was starting to lift.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqJ6LI_Yk7_text","label":"ggqJ6LI_Yk7_text","default":"<p><strong>Month 4: The Confidence Started Coming Back</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDB1I9aL_1_text","label":"ggDB1I9aL_1_text","default":"<p>By month 4, I was doing things I'd stopped doing.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS57mEwk1z_text","label":"ggS57mEwk1z_text","default":"<p><strong>I carried a full laundry basket up the stairs. Both hands. No fear.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIR3RvmLKy_text","label":"ggIR3RvmLKy_text","default":"<p>I reached up to get something from the top shelf without that moment of hesitation and mental calculation.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtSEizjuf1_text","label":"ggtSEizjuf1_text","default":"<p>I went for a hike with my sister. A real hike with elevation, not a gentle walk on flat ground.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdVZ6T6KCh_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggdVZ6T6KCh_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_83911s83911s8391.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggM-E8beuwQ_text","label":"ggM-E8beuwQ_text","default":"<p><strong>My daughter called and asked if I wanted to help her move furniture for her new apartment.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh-X0XQIoH_text","label":"ggh-X0XQIoH_text","default":"<p>A few months ago, I would have made an excuse. Now I said yes.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMvDDrWj5B_text","label":"ggMvDDrWj5B_text","default":"<p>The physical changes were obvious.</p><p>But the emotional shift was even bigger.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmBiSFyXZh_text","label":"ggmBiSFyXZh_text","default":"<p>I reached up to get something from the top shelf without that moment of hesitation and mental calculation.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2uOM2116Y_text","label":"gg2uOM2116Y_text","default":"<p><strong>I felt like myself again.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpwJ7b0AxK_text","label":"ggpwJ7b0AxK_text","default":"<p>Not some fragile version of myself. Not some old lady waiting to break.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggg2h2Oweu6_text","label":"ggg2h2Oweu6_text","default":"<p>Just... me. Sarah. The person I was before that devastating phone call.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gge4L-lMWQ2_text","label":"gge4L-lMWQ2_text","default":"<p>My adult son Hunter noticed it during Friday night dinner.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnBru7aSdU_text","label":"ggnBru7aSdU_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"Mom, you seem happier,\" he said. \"More like your old self.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3L8tjYKjW_text","label":"gg3L8tjYKjW_text","default":"<p>I didn't realize how much fear I'd been carrying until I finally let it go.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzTe1LCzVm_text","label":"ggzTe1LCzVm_text","default":"<p><strong>My Latest DEXA Scan That Made Me Cry</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggykf75_TqX_text","label":"ggykf75_TqX_text","default":"<p>My follow-up DEXA scan was scheduled for next February.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPo_4W5CmQ_text","label":"ggPo_4W5CmQ_text","default":"<p><strong>I was terrified the night before.</strong></p><p><strong>What if nothing had changed? What if I'd just wasted another 6 months?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggk5Vsz8shc_text","label":"ggk5Vsz8shc_text","default":"<p>What if my hope had been stupid and naive? The next morning, the technician did the scan.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggclCjlNQzk_text","label":"ggclCjlNQzk_text","default":"<p>Then my doctor came in to review the results.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6C5BRdUnX_text","label":"gg6C5BRdUnX_text","default":"<p><i><strong>She pulled up my scans side by side on the screen. My old scan from August last year. The new one from February.</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_jPC9kyPh_text","label":"gg_jPC9kyPh_text","default":"<p>Then my doctor came in to review the results.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmHq7l7r2p_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggmHq7l7r2p_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_hgcxnihgcxnihgcx.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCDAKces86_text","label":"ggCDAKces86_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"Sarah, your T-score improved to negative 1.9. You've gained bone density.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJDz23aFfO_text","label":"ggJDz23aFfO_text","default":"<p><strong>I started crying right there in her office.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggniS0cZmoY_text","label":"ggniS0cZmoY_text","default":"<p><i>\"How is this possible? You said just keep taking calcium...\"</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPzHI1G9Ix_text","label":"ggPzHI1G9Ix_text","default":"<p><strong>She looked genuinely surprised. \"What did you do? What changed?\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5bl0rRp3M_text","label":"gg5bl0rRp3M_text","default":"<p>I told her about Dr. Chen's research. About NAD+. About restoring cellular energy.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJpsBVUPZe_text","label":"ggJpsBVUPZe_text","default":"<p>She was quiet for a moment.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggu1yA2_MEl_text","label":"ggu1yA2_MEl_text","default":"<p><i>\"I don't know much about this approach,\" she admitted. \"But whatever you're doing, keep doing it. This is remarkable for someone your age going through menopause.\"</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkLnIGKx7B_text","label":"ggkLnIGKx7B_text","default":"<p><strong>I went from borderline osteoporosis back to moderate osteopenia in record time.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8SmwssvW__text","label":"gg8SmwssvW__text","default":"<p>My bones demolition crew was still active, but my bone's construction crew had finally woken up.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnGPid-ZCD_text","label":"ggnGPid-ZCD_text","default":"<p><strong>They had the energy to rebuild again.</strong></p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
  }
